<p><strong>SCP-5241：异界信息</strong><br />
<em>别放它出来。</em><br />
由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/placeholder-mcd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6536693); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6536693&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608737408" alt="Placeholder McD" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6536693)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/placeholder-mcd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6536693); return false;">Placeholder McD</a></span>代表队伍“.AIC（人工智障创作者）”为2020设定复兴竞赛而作。<br />
由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ryan-squirrel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2844977); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2844977&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608737408" alt="Ryan SQuirrel" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2844977)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ryan-squirrel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2844977); return false;">Ryan SQuirrel</a></span>与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zarthustra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2778191); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2778191&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608737408" alt="Zarthustra" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2778191)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zarthustra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2778191); return false;">Zarthustra</a></span>翻译。</p>
</div>
